<p class="contextTtl" id="p1" data-pid="1"><span id="page217" class="pageNum" aria-hidden="true" data-no="217" data-before-text="217"></span><strong>レッスン52</strong></p>
<h1 id="p2" data-pid="2"><strong>良い身だしなみは大切</strong></h1>
</header>	<div class="clearfix alternatePresentation clickable noTooltips
		">
		<div class="thumbnail">
			<img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1809" class="lightbox"
